data.description: Welcome to this stylish and comfortable home in the popular Bentwater community. This 4 bed/4.5 bath home boasts numerous tasteful finishes and recent updates. As you enter, the open foyer is flanked by a formal living room/office and dining room. The family room features a beautiful stone fireplace with wood mantel and an adjacent office/play space that can be closed off for privacy. The kitchen, which is seamlessly connected to the living area, is a sea of crisp white shaker cabinetry and marble countertops atop a massive island. The master suite upstairs is very large, with a separate cozy sitting area. The en suite bathroom has garden tub and separate shower, double sinks, water closet, and shiplap accents. There are three additional bedrooms and two bathrooms upstairs. The finished basement has a cabin-like feel with tongue and groove ceiling and hand-scraped hardwood floors. A full bathroom and plumbed space with potential for full kitchen round out this amazing space. Outside, the new massive Trex deck accommodates a large dining area and separate seating area. The area under the deck is rain proof for additional entertaining space or storage and includes an electrical connection to support a hot tub. The tiered backyard boasts a picturesque fire pit area with electrical connections, all overlooking peaceful Little Pumpkinvine Creek.
